    <item>
      <title>立法者希望拜登拒绝向中国无人机制造商大疆创新颁发出口许可证</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-want-biden-reject-export-licenses-chinese-drone-maker-dji-2023-12-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，由 15 名共和党议员组成的团体以国家安全为由，要求五角大楼阻止向中国无人机制造商大疆创新发放美国零部件的出口许可证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-want-biden-reject-export-licenses-chinese-drone-maker-dji-2023-12-18/</guid>
